# ADV-IA-43-003: OpenSSL CVE suppressions.
# Only valid for wasm32 target. If non-wasm builds added, remove these suppressions.
# The Workers runtime uses Web Crypto, not OpenSSL. The openssl crate is a
# transitive dependency pulled in for non-wasm build targets only and is never
# compiled into the production WASM bundle.
# Expires: 2026-08-25 - openssl crate CVEs not applicable to wasm32 target
